nodes.id: 中华人民共和国拉萨海关

zh-cn: 中华人民共和国拉萨海关

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国海关总署在拉萨市设立的直属海关，行政级别为正厅级，管辖范围为西藏自治区全境。
description.en: A directly affiliated customs office of the General Administration of Customs of the People's Republic of China located in Lhasa. It holds a departmental level administrative rank and its jurisdiction covers the entire Tibet Autonomous Region.

zh-cn: 中华人民共和国海关总署
en: General Administration of Customs of the People's Republic of China

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国国务院下属的，负责全国海关工作的正部级直属机构。
description.en: A ministry-level agency directly under the State Council of the People's Republic of China, responsible for customs administration nationwide.

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国拉萨海关关长、党委书记。

nodes.id: 中华人民共和国西藏地区人民海关

zh-cn: 中华人民共和国西藏地区人民海关
中华人民共和国西藏地区海关

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国拉萨海关的前身，于1962年成立。
description.en: The predecessor of Lhasa Customs of the People's Republic of China, established in 1962.

description.zh-cn: 1888年清朝与英属印度之间在锡金发生的战役。
description.en: A battle that occurred in 1888 in Sikkim between the Qing dynasty and British India.

description.zh-cn: 清朝政府与大英帝国签订的关于锡金和西藏的条约，条约决定开辟亚东为商埠。
description.en: A treaty signed between the Qing dynasty and the British Empire concerning Sikkim and Tibet, which stipulated the opening of Yadong as a trade port.

description.zh-cn: 最初根据《中英藏印条约》设立的海关，历史上曾多次开关和关闭。
description.en: A customs office originally established under the Convention of Calcutta, which has been opened and closed multiple times throughout history.

description.zh-cn: 英国外交官，曾长期担任清朝海关总税务司。
description.en: A British diplomat who served as the Inspector-General of the Chinese Maritime Customs Service for a long period.

description.zh-cn: 英国人，被赫德任命为首任亚东关税务总司。
description.en: A British national appointed by Robert Hart as the first commissioner of Yadong Customs.

description.zh-cn: 西藏的执政机构。
description.en: The governing council of Tibet.

description.zh-cn: 1959年在中国共产党主导下于西藏地区进行的土地改革运动。
description.en: The land reform movement carried out in the Tibet region in 1959 under the leadership of the Communist Party of China.

nodes.id: 中华人民共和国国务院

zh-cn: 中华人民共和国国务院
en: State Council of the People's Republic of China

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国最高国家行政机关。
description.en: The highest state administrative organ of the People's Republic of China.

description.zh-cn: 1962年中华人民共和国与印度之间因边界问题爆发的战争。
description.en: A war between the People's Republic of China and India in 1962 over their disputed border.

description.zh-cn: 1962年成立的海关，同年因中印边境战争关闭。
description.en: A customs office established in 1962 and closed the same year due to the Sino-Indian War.

description.zh-cn: 1975年在原噶尔昆沙海关基础上重新设立的海关，后更名为中华人民共和国狮泉河海关。
description.en: A customs office re-established in 1975 on the basis of the former Gar Kunsha Customs, later renamed Shiquanhe Customs of the People's Republic of China.

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国海关总署设于乌鲁木齐的直属海关。
description.en: A directly affiliated customs office of the General Administration of Customs of the PRC located in Ürümqi.

nodes.id: 中华人民共和国狮泉河海关

zh-cn: 中华人民共和国狮泉河海关

description.zh-cn: 由原普兰分关更名而来，隶属于拉萨海关。
description.en: Renamed from the former Pulan Branch Customs, it is subordinate to Lhasa Customs.

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国拉萨海关的下属海关。
description.en: A subordinate customs office of Lhasa Customs of the People's Republic of China.

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国拉萨海关的下属海关。
description.en: A subordinate customs office of Lhasa Customs of the People's Republic of China.

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国拉萨海关的下属海关。
description.en: A subordinate customs office of Lhasa Customs of the People's Republic of China.

zh-cn: 拉萨海关驻机场办事处
拉萨海关驻贡嘎机场办事处

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国拉萨海关的下属机构，负责拉萨贡嘎国际机场的海关业务。
description.en: A subordinate unit of Lhasa Customs of the People's Republic of China, responsible for customs operations at Lhasa Gonggar International Airport.

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国拉萨海关的下属海关，负责拉萨市、昌都市、山南市、那曲市除拉萨航空口岸外海关各类工作的执行。
description.en: A subordinate customs office of Lhasa Customs, responsible for executing various customs tasks in Lhasa, Chamdo, Shannan, and Nagqu, excluding the Lhasa air port.

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国拉萨海关的下属海关，主要负责林芝市境内海关业务。
description.en: A subordinate customs office of Lhasa Customs, primarily responsible for customs operations within Nyingchi City.

relationships.source: 中华人民共和国西藏地区人民海关
relationships.target: 中华人民共和国拉萨海关

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国拉萨海关于1974年成立，是中华人民共和国西藏地区人民海关的后继机构。
description.en: Lhasa Customs of the People's Republic of China was established in 1974 as the successor to the People's Customs of the Tibet Region of the People's Republic of China.

relationships.target: 中英藏印条约

description.zh-cn: 隆吐山战役后，清朝政府和大英帝国签订了《中英藏印条约》。
description.en: After the Battle of Lung-t'u-shan, the Qing government and the British Empire signed the Convention of Calcutta.

relationships.target: 大英帝国

description.zh-cn: 在1888年的隆吐山战役中，清朝政府与大英帝国（英属印度）处于敌对状态。
description.en: During the Battle of Lung-t'u-shan in 1888, the Qing government and the British Empire (British India) were in a state of hostility.

relationships.target: 亚东海关

description.zh-cn: 《中英藏印条约》决定开辟亚东为商埠，促成了亚东海关的正式开关。
description.en: The Convention of Calcutta stipulated the opening of Yadong as a trade port, which led to the official opening of Yadong Customs.

relationships.target: 赫德

description.zh-cn: 赫德任命戴乐尔为亚东关税务总司。
description.en: Robert Hart appointed F. E. Taylor as the Commissioner of Yadong Customs.

relationships.target: 亚东海关

description.zh-cn: 戴乐尔担任首任亚东关税务总司。
description.en: F. E. Taylor served as the first Commissioner of Yadong Customs.

relationships.target: 亚东海关

description.zh-cn: 1913年9月，噶厦政府关闭了亚东海关。
description.en: In September 1913, the Kashag government closed Yadong Customs.

relationships.target: 中华人民共和国西藏地区人民海关

description.zh-cn: 1959年西藏土地改革运动后，中华人民共和国国务院决定在西藏地区设立海关，促成了中华人民共和国西藏地区人民海关的成立。
description.en: After the Tibetan land reform movement in 1959, the State Council of the PRC decided to establish customs in the Tibet region, leading to the formation of the People's Customs of the Tibet Region of the PRC.

relationships.source: 中华人民共和国国务院
relationships.target: 中华人民共和国西藏地区人民海关

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国国务院于1959年决定在西藏地区设立海关。
description.en: The State Council of the People's Republic of China decided to establish customs in the Tibet region in 1959.

relationships.target: 亚东海关

description.zh-cn: 亚东海关于1962年中印边境战争后关闭。
description.en: Yadong Customs was closed after the 1962 Sino-Indian War.

relationships.target: 噶尔昆沙海关

description.zh-cn: 噶尔昆沙海关于1962年中印边境战争后关闭。
description.en: Gar Kunsha Customs was closed after the 1962 Sino-Indian War.

relationships.target: 普兰海关

description.zh-cn: 普兰海关（时称普兰分关）于1975年以原噶尔昆沙海关为基础重新设立。
description.en: Pulan Customs (then known as Pulan Branch) was re-established in 1975 on the basis of the former Gar Kunsha Customs.

relationships.target: 乌鲁木齐海关

description.zh-cn: 普兰海关在1975年至1979年期间由乌鲁木齐海关代管。
description.en: Pulan Customs was managed by Ürümqi Customs from 1975 to 1979.

relationships.target: 中华人民共和国拉萨海关

description.zh-cn: 1979年6月9日，普兰海关划归拉萨海关管理。
description.en: On June 9, 1979, Pulan Customs was transferred to the administration of Lhasa Customs.

relationships.target: 中华人民共和国狮泉河海关

description.zh-cn: 1984年5月24日，普兰海关更名为中华人民共和国狮泉河海关。
description.en: On May 24, 1984, Pulan Customs was renamed Shiquanhe Customs of the People's Republic of China.

relationships.source: 中华人民共和国狮泉河海关
relationships.target: 中华人民共和国拉萨海关

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国狮泉河海关（前身为普兰海关）隶属于拉萨海关。
description.en: Shiquanhe Customs of the People's Republic of China (formerly Pulan Customs) is subordinate to Lhasa Customs.

description.zh-cn: 日喀则海关是拉萨海关的下辖分关。

description.en: Jilong Customs is a subordinate branch of Lhasa Customs.

description.en: Since June 1984, Nyalam Customs has been a subordinate customs office of Lhasa Customs.

description.en: Lhasa Gonggar Airport Customs is a subordinate unit of Lhasa Customs.

description.zh-cn: 八廓海关是拉萨海关的下属海关。
description.en: Barkhor Customs is a subordinate customs office of Lhasa Customs.

description.zh-cn: 林芝海关是拉萨海关的下属海关。
description.en: Nyingchi Customs is a subordinate customs office of Lhasa Customs.

relationships.target: 中华人民共和国拉萨海关

description.zh-cn: 2019年5月1日重新成立的亚东海关隶属于拉萨海关。
description.en: The re-established Yadong Customs on May 1, 2019, is subordinate to Lhasa Customs.
